      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"healing\" thing doesn't really work though. i've been \"healing\" for months. it just feels like i'm dragging this heavy, empty shell of a person through a world i don't belong in anymore. everything i worked for was my purpose. without the research, without the career, i'm just... a ghost. i look at everyone else moving forward and i just feel like i'm stuck in a void. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to sleep and not wake up to this crushing weight every single morning.",
